The uMoya hitmaker took to Instagram on Tuesday evening to announce the birth of his son- his second with his partner Innocentia Morolong.The couple have decided to name their son Yuri.Posting a picture of himself holding his newborn son's hand, Heavy K wrote: "Once again the Lord has trusted me with one of his angels. Tonight my baby boy Yuri was born. Even words cant explain how I'm feeling right now."A photo posted by HEAVY-K THE DRUMBOSS (@heavykdrumboss) on Dec 20, 2016 at 11:55am PSTA photo posted by HEAVY-K THE DRUMBOSS (@heavykdrumboss) on Dec 20, 2016 at 11:55am PSTHeavy K and Innocentia's new bundle of joy joins his older brother who was born in October last year.